item.title: CVE-2022-26834|2024-08-03T05:11:44.548Z -- rakuten%20mobile%2C%20inc. -- rakuten%20casa
item.description: Improper access control vulnerability in Rakuten Casa version AP_F_V1_4_1 or AP_F_V2_0_0 allows a remote attacker to obtain the information stored in the product because the product is set to accept HTTP connections from the WAN side by default.
